uk.ac.ebi.ep.core.compare

Class ListComparison

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.ep.core.compare.AbstractComparison<List<?>>
      • uk.ac.ebi.ep.core.compare.ListComparison
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparison<List<?>>

    public class ListComparison
extends AbstractComparison<List<?>>
    Comparison for lists of items. It does not take into account their order, so for this class [ "1", "2" ] is not different from [ "2", "1" ].
    This comparison requires that the items class implements properly the equals and hashCode methods.
    Since:
    1.1.0
    Author:
    rafa
